{"tid":2272496,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國媒體爆料   iPad Pro 明年改用 mini LED 螢幕","createTime":"2020-11-05T05:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T09:49:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2b8e99aca851be35e81b83d13d7f4494700933","tid":2272496,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"今年年初 Apple 推出了新版本 iPad Pro，加入了 LiDAR 功能，韓國傳媒日前報導指，Apple 於明年年初會為 iPad Pro 推出小改版。新機的其中一個改進之處，就是採用量度更高、更慳電和沒有燒印問題的 mini LED 螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/pad/img/2020-11/05/68721/eprice_1_3fb7e4ad25e602089d65058b9a2f93ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fpad%2Fimg%2F2020-11%2F05%2F68721%2Feprice_1_3fb7e4ad25e602089d65058b9a2f93ff.jpg&h=24ea42d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導指 Apple 已經敲定 mini LED 螢幕的供應商，就是韓國的 LG Display，消息指 12.9 吋 iPad Pro 會率先採用 mini LED，然後就輪到 11 吋的版本；Apple 之後更會陸續為更多 iPad 平板、MacBook 筆電和 iMac 一體式電腦，改用 mini LED 螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Apple 的產品一向以螢幕質素作為賣點，不過他們在面對新螢幕技術時，通常都會傾向保守。從早前發表的 iPhone 12 才首次全系列採用 OLED 螢幕可見一斑，現階段 iPad、MacBook 和 iMac 改用 mini LED，似乎與 Apple 以往的做法有點不符。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4469/68721/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fpad%2Ftalk%2F4469%2F68721%2F1%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4GmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=41b0f31d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4469/68721/1/</a>"},{"pid":"cf9a379c191b5f721e7c5c3d7b99e4d82f86aefb","tid":2272496,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"未成熟嘅技術應該唔會用<br />\n一係apple 有份幫手研發 到幾成熟"},{"pid":"f645c804e8e2709ffb3aee81ab80b9fa5a918b6d","tid":2272496,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"係就好，推進下mini led發展，過多一兩年全線換晒mini led"},{"pid":"0076572c784083a87648786ecaeb141f79d81c09","tid":2272496,"uid":54452,"l